raw_hits.title: Census 2021, G53 Highest non-school qualification: level of education by industry of employment by sex, Significant Urban Areas (SUA)
raw_hits.description:
Highest non-school qualification: level of education by industry of employment by sex data for Significant Urban Areas (SUA), 2021 Census, Count of employed persons aged 15 years and over with a non-school qualification.
This table is based on place of usual residence.
Non-school qualifications are educational attainments other than those of a pre-primary, primary or secondary education level.
Excludes persons with a qualification outside the scope of the Australian Standard Classification of Education (ASCED).
Please note that there are small random adjustments made to all cell values to protect the confidentiality of data. These adjustments may cause the sum of rows or columns to differ by small amounts from table totals.
